rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0001
rows.name:
Now, the real question is
how we're going to reach
the Cliffs of Mors.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0002
rows.name:
I doubt we could convince any regular
sailor to take us there.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0003
rows.name:
No way they'd want to get anywhere near
the World Tree.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0004
rows.name:
In that case,
I shall arrange for a military vessel.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0005
rows.name:
It might be a bit of a detour,
but they're reliable and
will surely get us there.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0008
rows.name:
Heh...
It might be seen as
my abuse of power, though.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0009
rows.name:
So we need to go to the port at
Hadashal Palace in Superbia, right?

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0011
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi...
Could you contact them in advance?
